ZH: 工人们正在铺路修建新的高速公路。
EN: Workers are laying down the road to build a new highway.

ZH: 这个城市正在铺路以改善交通状况。
EN: This city is laying down roads to improve traffic conditions.

ZH: 我们需要铺路才能到达目的地。
EN: We need to lay down roads in order to reach our destination.

ZH: 铺路工程将在下周开始。
EN: The road construction project will begin next week.

ZH: 省政府计划在今年铺路一百公里。
EN: The provincial government plans to lay down one hundred kilometers of road this year.

ZH: 铺路的过程需要很多人力和物力。
EN: The process of road laying requires a lot of manpower and resources.

ZH: 这座小岛只有一条铺路，连接它和大陆。
EN: This small island only has one road that connects it to the mainland.

ZH: 这个村庄正在铺路，希望能吸引更多游客。
EN: This village is laying down roads in hopes of attracting more tourists.

ZH: 铺路需要精确的计划和施工。
EN: Laying down roads requires precise planning and construction.

ZH: 这段路是昨天才新铺的。
EN: This road was just laid down yesterday.

ZH: 铺路的材料必须经过检验才能使用。
EN: The materials for laying down roads must be inspected before use.

ZH: 城市正在逐步铺路改善市内交通。
EN: The city is gradually laying down roads to improve local traffic.

ZH: 这条路铺在了山脚下。
EN: This road is laid down at the foot of the mountain.

ZH: 我们花了一周时间来铺这条路。
EN: It took us a week to lay down this road.

ZH: 政府决定在这个区域铺路建设一所新学校。
EN: The government decided to lay down roads in this area to build a new school.

ZH: 这个地区的交通拥堵，需要铺路扩宽道路。
EN: The traffic in this area is congested, and road expansion is needed.

ZH: 铺路的工程比我们想象的要复杂。
EN: The road construction project is more complex than we imagined.

ZH: 铺路的费用预算已经超支。
EN: The budget for road construction has exceeded the estimates.

ZH: 城市规划部门计划在明年铺路一百公里。
EN: The city planning department plans to lay down one hundred kilometers of road next year.

ZH: 这个国家正在铺设高速铁路网。
EN: This country is laying down a high-speed railway network.
